  • public class ETTriggeredEmail
extends ETSoapObject
    An ETTriggeredEmail represents a Triggered Email in the Salesforce Marketing Cloud. A Triggered Email is... Triggered Emails are managed in the Marketing Cloud Email app under the "Interactions" menu: Terminology note: Triggered Emails are sometimes referred to as "Triggered Sends" in the Email app, and the SOAP API refers to Triggered Emails as "Triggered Send Definitions".
